HEADWORD: Dentist
<hw>Den"tist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From L.
<ets>dens</ets>, <ets>dentis</ets>, tooth: cf. F. <ets>dentiste</ets>.
See <er>Tooth</er>.]</ety> <def>One whose business it is to clean,
extract, or repair natural teeth, and to make and insert artificial
ones; a dental surgeon.</def></p>

